WEBVTT

00:06:58.542 --> 00:07:02.101
we will convert the super-spreaders
from the greatest barrier

00:07:02.125 --> 00:07:05.750
to the most powerful deployment
strategy that we can imagine.

00:07:08.583 --> 00:07:10.851
This is a radical concept.

00:07:10.875 --> 00:07:13.167
It has huge potential payoff,

00:07:14.375 --> 00:07:16.726
but there's a catch.

00:07:16.750 --> 00:07:18.167
And it's serious.

00:07:20.917 --> 00:07:24.375
Before we deploy a therapy
that may transmit,

00:07:25.792 --> 00:07:30.101
even if it's only in a limited population
of already infected individuals,